maxMsgNum &amp;gt;= nextMsgNum &amp;gt;= minMsgNum。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>cary huang: PostgreSQL’s Planner – Simple Scan Paths vs Plans</title><link>https://yangyingchao.github.io/postgr.es_p_6s9/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>yang.yingchao@qq.com (yc)</author><guid>https://yangyingchao.github.io/postgr.es_p_6s9/</guid><description>&lt;div class="ox-hugo-toc toc has-section-numbers"&gt;
